dotbpe是一款基于CSharp编写的RPC框架，但是它的目标不仅仅只是解决rpc的问题，而是解决整个业务解决方案的问题，封装在常见的项目产品开发中的通用组件，让开发人员只专注于开发业务逻辑代码。底层通信默认实现基于DotNetty，可替换成其他Socket通信组件。dotbpe使用的默认协议名称叫Amp,编解码使用谷歌的Protobuf3,不过这些默认实现都是可以替换的。

Json and Xml Serializer for .NET projects

Support :
* Wpf, Windows Forms, Asp.Net
* Uwp (>=build 16299)
* Asp.Net Core, Xamarin (.Net Standard 2.0)
* etc.

* JsonO 
    * Methods 
        * ToJson: Object (object or dynamic) => Json 
        * FromJson: Json => Object (type or dynamic) 
        * ToXml: Object (object or dynamic) => Xml  
        * FromXml: Xml => Object (type or dynamic) 
    * Serialization Settings : Formatting, indentation, preserve circular reference, date format string (default: ISO), culture (default: InvariantCulture)
    * DefaultTypeResolver Settings: Naming Strategy (camel case, snake case or create a custom naming strategy), include Fields, include private/ non Public fields and properties, provider type to optimize object creation and getter/setter (dynamic by default, expression, reflection)
* Converters: default converters (object, ExpandoObject, enumerable, dictionary, primitive) or register / override a custom converter (with ConverterResolver)
* JsonTextReader and JsonTextWriter: allow to read and write Json
* Services: (for IoC containers)
   * JsonSerializationService (IJsonSerializationService)

    * Serialization Settings : Formatting, indentation, preserve circular reference, date format string (default: ISO), culture (default: InvariantCulture)
    * DefaultTypeResolver Settings: Naming Strategy (camel case, snake case or create a custom naming strategy), include Fields, include private/ non Public fields and properties, provider type to optimize object creation and getter/setter (dynamic by default, expression, reflection)
* Converters: default converters (object, ExpandoObject, enumerable, dictionary, primitive) or register / override a custom converter (with ConverterResolver)
* JsonTextReader and JsonTextWriter: allow to read and write Json
* Services: (for IoC containers)
   * JsonSerializationService (IJsonSerializationService)

Spire.PDF for .NET is a versatile PDF library that enables software developers to generate, edit, read and manipulate PDF files within their own .NET applications. As a standalone PDF component, Spire.PDF for .NET provides users an incredible wealth of features without installing Adobe Acrobat. This component is completely written in C#, but also supports VB.NET, Windows Forms and ASP.NET. 
With the Spire.PDF for .NET API, you can get the ability to read PDF text and image even attachments with high efficiency. Even the special content such as language written from right to left can be extracted such as Herbrew and Arabic. Other basic features such as text, image, table, shapes, hyperlinks, bookmark, headings, footnotes, lists, form fields, pagination, booklet barcode, attachments, transparency, annotations, actions, overlay etc all work great for users. As for security, Spire.PDF for .NET enables you to protect your PDF files by passwords and digital signature.
